name: Dandy Oval Chest
description: The Dandy oval chest of drawers by Kifu Paris features an elegant design, inlaid in cream shagreen with bronze-patina brass details. This luxurious home accent includes three drawers and interiors inlaid in gemelina wood veneer. Available in light grey shagreen and parchment, the piece can be custom sized and finished upon request, and is handcrafted in the Philippines.
